TextEng: Are you a prisoner here?
Stand back! I'll have no tricks out of you!
Calm down. I'm certainly not with Kurth.
You kept in prison?
Stand back! No tricks!!
Me not with Kurth. You calm down now.
Of course I'm not here to punish you.
Text: 물론 널 벌주러 온 게 아니야.

TextEng: Me not here to punish, no.
Text: 벌 주러 온 거 아니야, 아니야.

TextEng: How do I know you're actually a prisoner, that this isn't some ruse?
Text: 네가 진짜 수감자인지, 이게 함정이 아닌지 어떻게 알아?

TextEng: I'd appreciate some information, first.
What reward would I get for letting you go?
Text: 널 놔주면 뭘 받을 수 있는데?

TextEng: Would you be able to find your way out on your own?
I'm not here to rescue you. Get out of my way.
Text: 널 구하러 온 게 아니야. 비켜.

TextEng: How I knows you not lying?
Me have questions, first.
Is there reward for letting you go?
You find way out on own?
Me no rescuer. Get lost.
I never said that. Killing is fun! Ha ha ha!!
Text: 그런 말 안 했는데. 죽이는 건 재밌거든! 하하하!!

TextEng: Why would I hurt you? Go, I said.
I don't know. Is there anything in it for me for helping you?
Text: 글쎄. 널 도와주면 내게 뭐가 있는데?

TextEng: Never say that! Hurting fun! HA ha Ha!!
Text: 그런 말 안 해! 아프게 하는 거 재밌어! 하하하!!

TextEng: Why me hurt you? Go, I say.
Don't know. What in it for me?
I don't trust you. Time to die!
No believe! Die! Die!!
Yes, I could use some information.
You're of no use to me. Get lost.
Yes, tell me. That good.
You no use to me, then. Go.
Then flee to safety. The way behind me is clear.
Text: 그럼 안전한 곳으로 도망쳐. 내 뒤로 가는 길은 깨끗해.

TextEng: Perhaps you should accompany me. It would be safer that way.
Text: 나랑 같이 가는 게 좋겠어. 그게 더 안전할 거야.

TextEng: Then run. Way behind is clear.
No, you come with me. Safer.
Text: 아니, 나랑 같이 가. 더 안전해.

TextEng: Just how did you end up prisoner here?
What do you know about this place?
Tell me what you know about Kurth.
All right. I'm done with you now.
How you end up in prison?
What you know of this place?
What you know of Kurth?
Me done with you.
But why wouldn't he just kill you?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Do you have any clue as to what might have caused his madness?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그가 미친 원인에 대해 짐작 가는 게 있어?

TextEng: Do you know where Kurth is?
What sorts of allies does Kurth have?
Are there any other prisoners?
Why they keep you alive?
Me look for Kurth.
What kind of friends Kurth have?
You see other prisoners?
What you knows about portal?
Tell me what you know about this portal.
Text: 이 차원문에 대해 아는 거 말해봐.
